column5: I had a great time last year and though I did rather well for my first time. I'm sure I can be challenging for first this year instead of 4th. LOL  Who was it that organized it last year?  I thought I should just start one.  Group number is 39168 and password is OFC
OK I did it group # is 39168 and password is OFC.  Come on now we need a dozen or so to make it fun.
not as big a race fan as some, but would still like to join, if it's OK, but don't know what site to go to
Yeah what's the website where we can sign up?

LOL that's funny, I guess the old guys know it was on yahoo.  Yahoo fantasy auto racing sign up page  Everyone is welcome to join in. It's just for fun, and it makes watching races a bit more interesting.
Okay, I'm in... I haven't followed nascar for years, maybe this will renew my interest. So far I'm in second place behind "Trophy Musky Chasers"
I`m in....  No idea who I`m picking but I`ll give it a go for fun....   Doug
I may or may not have signed up, or picked real drivers.  thanks for setting it up.
